Cumulative Sales

Cumulative sales are calculated using the SUM() window function, providing a running total of sales per employee over time.

Monthly Sales Leaders

Sales leaders for each month are ranked using a Common Table Expression (CTE) and the RANK() window function, identifying top performers each month.

